repeat what I said.

957
01:02:03,561 --> 01:02:07,265
- I've got it!
- Please, repeat precisely.

958
01:02:07,265 --> 01:02:11,258
"Hello, I'm calling
for Mr. Roussin.

959
01:02:12,336 --> 01:02:15,206
He's on a plane,
and has a message for you."

960
01:02:15,206 --> 01:02:17,108
