"Brochant knows everything."

962
01:02:18,976 --> 01:02:22,969
- No, repeat it!
- Come on, he's not stupid!

963
01:02:24,448 --> 01:02:28,286
"Brochant knows everything."

964
01:02:28,286 --> 01:02:31,956
Then you say,
"He knows about his wife."

965
01:02:31,956 --> 01:02:34,225
If Meneaux asks
who's speaking, you say,

966
01:02:34,225 --> 01:02:38,218
"A friend of Roussin's.
Brochant's coming with three pals."

967
01:02:40,698 --> 01:02:44,691
