of his toughest pals."

968
01:02:46,037 --> 01:02:49,173
- He's talented!
- I'm just parroting.

969
01:02:49,173 --> 01:02:52,410
- He's excellent!
- Could I improvise a bit?

970
01:02:52,410 --> 01:02:54,045
No!

971
01:02:54,045 --> 01:02:56,213
Don't shout!
You scared me!

972
01:02:56,213 --> 01:02:58,516
