973
01:02:58,516 --> 01:03:01,352
Come on,
we're wasting time!

974
01:03:01,352 --> 01:03:05,356
What's the number?

975
01:03:05,356 --> 01:03:09,349
01.47.47.39.63.

976
01:03:12,697 --> 01:03:15,366
- Here we go!
- I'm scared.

977
01:03:15,366 --> 01:03:19,036
- The strategy's fine.
- I'm worried about the executor.

978
01:03:19,036 --> 01:03:23,029
- It's ringing!
- Loudspeaker!

979
01:03:24,375 --> 01:03:28,368
